{"tid":271451,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"長榮取消港台線熱餐","createTime":"2017-06-05T05:57:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-26T17:31:09.000Z","uid":6604,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1a5191c7f3a6eb72485a94566c56e2164731f93a","tid":271451,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T05:57:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.evaair.com/zh-tw/about-eva-air/news/news-releases/2017/2017-05-25-inflight_cuisine.html?filter=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.evaair.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fabout-eva-air%2Fnews%2Fnews-releases%2F2017%2F2017-05-25-inflight_cuisine.html%3Ffilter%3D&d=XNtAwD5yvMaNfXBIg6XGQv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=b21af498\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.evaair.com/zh-tw/about-eva-air/news/news-releases/2017/2017-05-25-inflight_cuisine.html?filter=</a><br />\n<br />\n長榮航空機上餐飲及服務用品不斷推陳出新，6月1日起港澳與沖繩航線將提供新鮮現做、冷藏直送上機的糕點，在炎炎夏日來臨之際，讓旅客可以享受到新鮮、清爽的機上餐點。此外，機上也陸續提供各式養生食材以及茶飲，廣受好評的RIMOWA過夜包自5月中旬亦將陸續更換新款經典色系，讓搭機的民眾耳目一新。<br />\n<br />\n炎炎夏天的到來影響旅客胃口，航程短、航班多數落於非用餐時間的港澳與沖繩航線，在餐點上的設計更是需要費盡心思，因此長榮空廚特別設計蝦仁乳酪烤蛋派、培根鮮蔬鹹蛋糕、桂圓蛋糕、蜜汁火腿酥等各式糕點，低溫冷藏直送上機，讓食物保有美味的口感，營養也更加分。"},{"pid":"4c92592ad49a55b4f5b6b2f13484c29b75480c7a","tid":271451,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T05:59:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e72ff7cd531b85b246669b84ba4eb42f30753c4b","tid":271451,"uid":39012,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T05:59:54.000Z","msg":"Pr 的重要性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n語言藝術"},{"pid":"cb5bc60c386cbb76674b87cdae2bb7e5d003e02f","tid":271451,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T06:00:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Pr 的重要性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 