"},{"pid":"777cf1d0b3d7508791a1f6a188bd4c722d5ae284","tid":271451,"uid":13809,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T07:16:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Aviation/M.1496568678.A.C81.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FAviation%2FM.1496568678.A.C81.html&d=XNtAwD5yvMaNfXBIg6XGQv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=1aed6008\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Aviation/M.1496568678.A.C81.html</a><br />\n<br />\nptt 有埋相睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌，原來台灣人都係叫因航<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30df2f9d93bfd86aa089dfe849a9467ddc066100","tid":271451,"uid":6337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T07:19:54.000Z","msg":"屌真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以後要轉搭華航？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"333e00e4b5c71cb39a86685265aa861650b3cd99","tid":271451,"uid":78273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T07:22:25.000Z","msg":"香港台灣線，其實冇咩所謂<br />\n訓一陣就到"},{"pid":"4f4649f652ff36c7a40199080e8038fc39696328","tid":271451,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T07:27:48.000Z","msg":"1粒幾鐘訓陣都到"},{"pid":"7ddb061df1abf7d42a97a60670e98393d25fc8e4","tid":271451,"uid":8420,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T07:31:41.000Z","msg":"飛機餐都爭住食 食開屎咩"},{"pid":"61ef74a1ef85c50c43433ed14bf4b70d8fe8b031","tid":271451,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T07:39:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1粒幾鐘訓陣都到</blockquote><br />\n真係一套戲長少少都未完就落機"},{"pid":"579a96d5dc1706ed55b017f7375d305b6a1577d9","tid":271451,"uid":30006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T07:44:33.000Z","msg":"其實唔撚洗啦得一粒鐘"},{"pid":"b3ce3cf15256f9eef8dd2977d5f7b9fd77d31d25","tid":271451,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T08:04:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以後要轉搭華航？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n華航？提供似屎一樣既餐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n白膠槳狀態既餸汁<br />\n黏狀飯<br />\n<br />\n唯一係空姐斟既烏龍茶是仍然好味<br />\n（唔排除係因為空氣乾所以覺得茶好味）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大約五六年前，華航個餐是好正的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2ed8a3ece128ea514ec48ddbd6ca867cd1cee46","tid":271451,"uid":5392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T08:50:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以後要轉搭華航？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n華航？提供似屎一樣既餐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n白膠槳狀態既餸汁<br />\n黏狀飯<br />\n<br />\n唯一係空姐斟既烏龍茶是仍然好味<br />\n（唔排除係因為空氣乾所以覺得茶好味）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大約五六年前，華航個餐是好正的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今日華航去台北 杞子冬菇雞肉飯 椰汁糕 水<br />\n個雞肉好滑 好正常 係個椰汁糕有d硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1e7d3c1a5782d5a653ec4a3a08f9fb8f34df947","tid":271451,"uid":82994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T05:12:11.000Z","msg":"還我熱餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我一路都好想食長榮飛機餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c5f064192e9793ec2144d240616022929ecd294","tid":271451,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T05:28:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以後要轉搭華航？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n華航？提供似屎一樣既餐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n白膠槳狀態既餸汁<br />\n黏狀飯<br />\n<br />\n唯一係空姐斟既烏龍茶是仍然好味<br />\n（唔排除係因為空氣乾所以覺得茶好味）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大約五六年前，華航個餐是好正的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今日華航去台北 杞子冬菇雞肉飯 椰汁糕 水<br />\n個雞肉好滑 好正常 係個椰汁糕有d硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個飯你接受到？<br />\n<br />\n我兩次都是近似文具店既槳糊加白膠槳混合物<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc5a7b283fbd11ba6023fb80b886df147244e929","tid":271451,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T05:32:31.000Z","msg":"長榮重點是空姐。  <br />\n<br />\n可否幫佢地換裝， 著T shirt,  熱褲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dd9da1b8a4d1b8961c94f5283b1442d19056464","tid":271451,"uid":21035,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T05:38:29.000Z","msg":"紅隧/屯門公路炒車塞車個車程分分鐘仲耐過飛台灣啦，你唔屌九巴唔派餐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81036b22cd2c3dc7db46bdda856069c944d0e036","tid":271451,"uid":148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T05:44:38.00